Set up JS compiler for sublime

Node:
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install nodejs

Location:
/home/ghostman/.config/sublime-text-3/Packages/User/Node.sublime-build 

Specification:
{
    "cmd": ["node", "$file", "$file_base_name"],
    "working_dir": "${project_path:${folder}}",
    "selector": "*.js"
}